ay\nproceedings and submit the case with a brief report explaining its nature to the sessions\njudge or to such other magistrate having jurisdiction as the sessions judge directs.\n(2) the magistrate to whom the case is submitted may if so empowered either try the\ncase himself or send the case for trial to the court of session or the high court.",
